		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Speak to Marlono Rhandle - S_GLO_IronThrone_Group3_Prisoner2 926d2515-b22a-4b51-8737-42a6c1ebd4f4 - (37; 39; 49) in the Dock warehouse after saving them.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Quick setup:&#xD;&#xA;- Load CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use Debug Book (Ctrl + Shift + 9)&#xD;&#xA;- Set Quest Flags and Options -&gt; Act3 (LOW) -&gt; Iron Throne -&gt; Change State -&gt; Back At Docks -&gt; MajoritySaved&#xD;&#xA;- Then talk to the NPC" />
